      "message": "IMO this is a case where simple lambda expressions make the code easier to read and less verbose. Unless there\u0027s a \"hard\" technical reason to not use lambdas (like one of the target compilers doesn\u0027t support them) I don\u0027t think we should settle for ugly code just for the sake of convention. I think we should revisit our stance on lambdas...",
